  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_828672\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2507889_828672\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481828\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2507889_481828\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Self-guided Field Trips</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2507894\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Trail-of-Time-walkway.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"A concrete walkway next to the rim of the canyon with people walking along it\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Trail-of-Time-walkway.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Trail of Time walkway\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption><p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>If you are organizing your own class field trip to the park, the following resources will help in planning your visit. If you need further assistance, please <a href=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=65B5E884BAE18C9DAB9E17BAFA16BFA4499366814CA5C2985009&amp;r=/grca/learn/education/self-guided-field-trips.htm\" id=\"/common/utilities/sendmail/sendemail.cfm?o=65B5E884BAE18C9DAB9E17BAFA16BFA4499366814CA5C2985009&amp;r=/grca/learn/education/self-guided-field-trips.htm|\">contact us</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span>Educational Fee Waiver:</span></strong> You may be eligible to receive an entrance fee waiver for your class. To apply for a waiver, <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/educational-fee-waiver.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/educational-fee-waiver.htm|\">click here</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Self Guided Activities:</strong> Bring your students to the Grand Canyon! Grand Canyon National Park is an awe-inspiring place for visitors of all ages, with educational opportunities to be found around every corner. Y<span style=\"text-align: -webkit-match-parent;\">ou can use the following activities to lead students through an engaging and educational visit to the park! Find Geology and Ecology activities below.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Activities:</strong> Browse our <a href=\"/grca/learn/education/student-report-information.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6777956,/grca/learn/education/student-report-information.htm,14078|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">at home activities and resources</a> for content information and activity ideas before and after your field trip.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Background Information:</strong> Learn about the <a href=\"/grca/learn/nature/grca-geology.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5752117,grca-geology.htm,14077|\">geology</a>, <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/naturescience/index.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/naturescience/index.htm|\">science</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/historyculture/index.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/historyculture/index.htm|\">history</a> of Grand Canyon.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Trip Planning:</strong> View <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/index.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/index.htm|\">Plan Your Visit</a> for maps, directions and other trip planning assistance.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7142252\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7142252\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-4E87A7A1-FCA5-EED3-70F6CAC21C3641B5\">\n<h2>Teacher-led Trips</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-4